# DO-254 Traceability

## Overview

Traceability matrix linking hardware requirements, design, verification per DO-254.

## Traceability Structure

```json
{
  "do254_trace": {
    "version": "1.0",
    "baseline": "IBL-2024-Q3",
    "date": "2024-09-25",
    "traces": [
      {
        "requirement_id": "HW-REQ-001",
        "description": "AFDX switch redundancy",
        "dal": "A",
        "hdl_files": [
          "afdx-switch/rtl/redundancy_manager.vhdl",
          "afdx-switch/rtl/failover_controller.vhdl"
        ],
        "test_cases": [
          "HW-TC-001",
          "HW-TC-002"
        ],
        "verification_status": "PASS"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

## Verification by DAL

- **DAL A**: Full verification per DO-254 Table A-1
- **DAL B**: Verification per DO-254 Table A-1 (reduced)
- **DAL C/D**: Simplified verification

## Hardware Verification Tools

- **HDL Simulator**: ModelSim (DO-254 qualified)
- **Synthesis**: Synopsys Design Compiler
- **Formal Verification**: Cadence JasperGold

